CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 9, 1966, pg. 2A reads: "Planning Health-O-Rama - Pittsburgh clergymen are shown mapping plans to contact churches in the area regarding assistance to help promote forthcoming Health-O-Rama to be held at the Savoy Ballroom, April 14-17. From left are, Rev. Charles Foggie, Msgr. Paul Bassompierre and Rev. James Cox. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Rev. Charles Foggie, Msgr. Paul Bassompierre, and Rev. James Cox, gathered around desk in office planning church participation in Health-O-Rama
